snippet.textDisplay: I'm in so much love with Dipali Vyas, the rightmost girl in the chorus. Her whole vibe is making me fall in love. Her magical eyes, her contagious smile is so different. Everytime the camera is on her, she does something with her eyes or her smile that give butterflies in my stomach 😂 Her style with the 'aawwoah', 'hay hay haiyyah', hand movements, sooo cute man. I can't express. Was looking at her the whole time even when she was out of focus. Don't know the last time when I felt so amazed seeing such mesmerising woman. I would do anything for her to see that natural cute smile on her face, that smile can heal anything! If you're reading this, say hi xD and if her bf/husband is reading this, dude, better protect her smile. Always smile like this. ❤️
